reviews.text: Excellent dim sum restaurant in the mall on the lower floor.  Food is outstanding and good service. Price range is very reasonable. Highly recommended

The restaurant is short-staffed and the food is of average quality.
Don't expect much. You have come to the right place if you are looking for a quite place for lunch/dinner in weekdays.
Dim sum is not bad, easy to access from carpark, with parking voucher

Tao Heung Restaurant is a famous chain store. This restaurant only occupied 50% of the total area of the previous Maxim restaurant. This new one is not very good in taste and services. So most of the time it's not full. For some dishes, it's good, for example, BBQ Pork, Steam Chicken, Steam Fish etc. For dim sum, it's too small in portion and most dim sum are delivered from central kitchen of the group. They are re-heat by people working in kitchen.
Good standard food and services

reviews.text: 센트럴에서 37B 버스를 타고 내린 아파트내 상가. 오후 늦은 시간이라서 저녁 식사 겸해서 한잔 하려고 슈퍼마켓에서 시원한 맥주를 한캔 사고, 푸드 카니발 층 牛什専家 라는 가게에서 안주로, 홍콩에서 맛들인 벌집위와 도가니 등이 들어있는 招牌牛三寶 라는 안주를 주문해서 시원하게 한잔 함. 맛있었음~ 맥주 대신에 바이주를 마셨어도 좋았을 것 같음. ^^
企堂服務差👎
5掂商場，冷氣不足，無乜野賣，太舊，垃圾中，5星星。
一個好過無既商場，應該唔會餓死！
乘車方便，大巴，小巴都有。轉乘地鉄也ok。广場有小吃街和超市，整体ok。
